OL,6,FValdo Calocane had an extensive track
OL,7,Frecord before he was charged with the
OL,8,Fkillings of three people in
OL,9,FNottingham, as Social Affairs
OL,10,FCorrespondent Stacey Foster reports
OL,12,FThere was relief on the morning of
OL,13,FJune 13, 2023, when police announced
OL,14,Fthey had arrested a suspect in
OL,15,Fconnection with the brutal killings of
OL,16,Fthree innocent people in city centre.
OL,18,FBut what we did not know at the time
OL,19,Fwas that Valdo Calocane was already a
OL,20,Fwanted man.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/30
