OL,6,FIn fact, had already been on the run
OL,7,Ffor nine months after assaulting a
OL,8,Ffemale police officer in 2021.
OL,10,FWhat is perhaps even more alarming is
OL,11,Fthat mental health services in the
OL,12,Fcity had also lost track of Calocane.
OL,14,FThe 33-year-old was a paranoid
OL,15,Fschizophrenic, known to mental health
OL,16,Fservices since 2020.
