OL,6,FHe had admitted to professionals that
OL,7,Fhe was no longer taking his medication
OL,8,Fin 2021, was arrested on multiple
OL,9,Foccasions after acts of violence, and
OL,10,Fwas sectioned under the Mental Health
OL,11,FAct four times.
OL,13,FHe even visited MI5 in London to "hand
OL,14,Fhimself in". Mental health
OL,15,Fprofessionals had not seen Calocane
OL,16,Fsince March 2022, when he was reviewed
OL,17,Fat a discharge clinic.
OL,19,FHis extensive track record raises many
OL,20,Fquestions for the authorities that
OL,21,Fexist to keep us all safe.
