OL,6,FBefore Calocane was due to be
OL,7,Fsentenced on January 25 for killing
OL,8,Fthree people and injuring three
OL,9,Fothers, Assistant Chief Constable of
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Police Rob Griffin
OL,11,Fgave an interview where he said: "My
OL,12,Fhonest assessment is no, I don't think
OL,13,Fwe could have done anything that would
OL,14,Fhave made any difference and would
OL,15,Fhave prevented what happened on that
OL,16,Fday."
