OL,6,FLess than a week later, Mr Griffin
OL,7,Fadmitted to ITV News that more should
OL,8,Fhave been done, but that it was still
OL,9,Fhis assessment that it would not have
OL,10,Fchanged the outcome.
OL,12,FHe said: "I have personally reviewed
OL,13,Fthis matter and we should have done
OL,14,Fmore to arrest him.
OL,16,F"However, because of the circumstance
OL,17,Fprevailing, at the time of the alleged
OL,18,Fassault, in my opinion it is highly
OL,19,Funlikely that he would have received a
OL,20,Fcustodial sentence.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/30
