OL,6,F"Of course, an arrest might have
OL,7,Ftriggered a route back into mental
OL,8,Fhealth services, but as we have seen
OL,9,Ffrom his previous encounters with
OL,10,Fthose services, it seems unlikely that
OL,11,Fhe would have engaged in this process."
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police has not
OL,14,Freferred itself to the Independent
OL,15,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) on
OL,16,Fthis failure at the time of writing.
