OL,6,F"In relation to the brief pursuit
OL,7,Fbefore we detained Calocane we did
OL,8,Fmake a referral to the IOPC,"
OL,9,FAssistant Chief Constable Griffin's
OL,10,Fstatement added.
OL,12,F"I can confirm that in relation to the
OL,13,Fmatter concerning the warrant, we
OL,14,Ffollowed the IOPC's guidance and,
OL,15,Fhaving shared details with them, we
OL,16,Fundertook professional discussions to
OL,17,Festablish whether the referral
OL,18,Fcriteria was met.
