OL,9,Freview of this matter."
OL,11,FCalocane was born in Guinnea-Bissau.
OL,12,FHis family moved to Madeira when he
OL,13,Fwas three-years-old and then to
OL,14,FLisbon, Portugal, when he was eight.
OL,15,FHe came to the UK in 2007 when he was
OL,16,F16-years-old.
OL,18,FHe had significant contact with mental
OL,19,Fhealth services in Nottingham before
OL,20,Fthe killings on June 13, 2023.
