OL,6,FHe was arrested for causing criminal
OL,7,Fdamage. An assessment under the Mental
OL,8,FHealth Act (MHA) concluded that he was
OL,9,Fpsychotic, but that the risk to others
OL,10,Fwas low, and that he should be
OL,11,Freferred, in the first instance, to
OL,12,Fthe Crisis Team for review at home.
OL,14,FHe was released without charge. Upon
OL,15,Freturning to his apartment an hour
OL,16,Flater, he knocked down another door to
OL,17,Fa different apartment in the block.
OL,19,FMay 25, 2020
