OL,6,FCalocane was detained under the MHA
OL,7,Fand admitted to Highbury Hospital
OL,8,Fafter being arrested for criminal
OL,9,Fdamage.
OL,11,FHe was treated with an anti-psychotic
OL,12,Fmedication and discharged on June 17,
OL,13,F2020 to the care of the Nottingham
OL,14,FCity Crisis Team.
OL,16,FHe was advised to take the medication
OL,17,Ffor a minimum of six to nine months,
OL,18,Fand to seek medical advice if he
OL,19,Fwished to stop taking it.
OL,21,FJuly 14 and July 31, 2020
