OL,7,FHospital after forcing his way into a
OL,8,Fflat having stopped taking his
OL,9,Fmedication.
OL,11,FThis was the third apartment in the
OL,12,Fsame block to which he attempted to
OL,13,Fgain forced entry.
OL,15,FThe anti-psychotic medication was
OL,16,Frestarted and increased. Thereafter,
OL,17,Fhe was managed in the community by the
OL,18,FEarly Intervention in Psychosis team.
OL,20,FHis medication was increased twice.
