OL,6,FThis all bears a striking resemblance
OL,7,Fto a similar incident I reported on
OL,8,Ffor ITV News in September 2020, just
OL,9,Fas we were coming out of the first
OL,10,Fwave of the coronavirus pandemic, and
OL,11,Fshops and bars were starting to reopen.
OL,13,FEight people were stabbed in
OL,14,FBirmingham City Centre. I remember
OL,15,Fthat Sunday morning walking around the
OL,16,Fcity, counting the various different
OL,17,Fcrime scenes scattered all over.
