OL,6,FA paranoid schizophrenic, Zephaniah
OL,7,FMcLeod, who had recently been released
OL,8,Ffrom prison, and was known to mental
OL,9,Fheath services, attacked people at
OL,10,Frandom. Among them was a group of
OL,11,Ffriends on a night out - for some of
OL,12,Fthem it was their first visit to the
OL,13,Fcity.
OL,15,FJacob Billington was killed and his
OL,16,Fbest friend Michael Callaghan was left
OL,17,Fwith life changing injuries.
