OL,6,FIt's been two years since I last saw
OL,7,FMichael, and while he has made
OL,8,Fsignificant steps in his recovery, he
OL,9,Fspoke to me about the challenges of
OL,10,Fhearing what happened in Nottingham.
OL,12,F'He was already in prison. All they
OL,13,Fhad to do to keep the public safe was
OL,14,Fnothing. It would have saved Jacob's
OL,15,Flife,' Michael Callaghan told ITV News
OL,17,FMichael's Mum, Anne Callaghan, says
OL,18,Frisk assessments are still not working
OL,19,Fto keep the public safe.
