OL,6,F'If you could read some of the things
OL,7,FI've read about the person who
OL,8,Fattacked Michael you'd just be
OL,9,Fabsolutely astonished that he was
OL,10,Fallowed to be out and about,' Anne
OL,11,FCallaghan told ITV News
OL,13,FIn the case of Zephaniah McLeod, a
OL,14,Freview took more than two years to be
OL,15,Fdelivered to the families and even now
OL,16,Fthey are still in search of answers as
OL,17,Fto what went wrong and what will
OL,18,Fchange.
