OL,6,FA coroner's inquest into Mr
OL,7,FBillington's death will start in
OL,8,FFebruary 2024, almost four years after
OL,9,Fhe was killed.
OL,11,FThe charity Rethink says the facts of
OL,12,Fthis case show we also need to reform
OL,13,Fthe MHA, which the government has
OL,14,Fpromised, but, so far not delivered.
OL,16,FThe chief executive of the charity
OL,17,FRethink described the system that
OL,18,Fcaters for mental health concerns in
OL,19,Fthe UK as 'incredibly badly stretched'
