OL,6,FRethink chief executive Brian Dow told
OL,7,FITV News: "Society also requires a
OL,8,Fsafety net and that's why we need to
OL,9,Fhave provision to detain people if
OL,10,Fthey are very very unwell and a risk
OL,11,Fto themselves or to others.
OL,13,F"And the Mental Health Act is a number
OL,14,Fof decades old. It's very out of date,
OL,15,Fit should have been making its way
OL,16,Fthrough parliament now.
